TY  - JOUR
T1  - Choosing the Devil You Don’t Know: Evidence for Limited Sensitivity to Sample Size–Based Uncertainty When It Offers an Advantage
AU  - Kutzner, Florian L.
AU  - Read, Daniel
AU  - Stewart, Neil
AU  - Brown, Gordon
